1. Activate the mod_communication Module from Zotonic Admin and restart zotonic to start the gen_server.

2. To create conference call do the following.
   PhoneList = ["3522192940", "3522469644"],
   if you want custom invite message then call
      m_communication:make_custom_template(Your_Message) which will make a custom_invite.tpl in templates folder
      Url = "custom_invite".
   if you want default invite template 
      Url = "inivite"
   m_communication:create_call(PhoneList, Url, Context).

3. To send sms to List of Phone Numbers.
   PhoneList = ["3522192940", "3522469644"],
   m_communication:send_sms(PhoneList, Message, Context).

4. To send Email to List of Email Ids.
   EmailList = ["sanketgawade7@gmail.com", "jeff@5nineshq.com"],
   m_communication:send_email(EmailList, Template, Vars, Context).
   
